Sentencas: The anode-supported BaCe0.48Zr0.4Yb0.1Co0.02O3-delta (BCZYC2)-based proton-conducting solid oxide fuel cells (H+-SOFCs) were fabricated using dual layer tape casting technique.
Titulo: Properties and Performance of Anode-Supported Proton-Conducting BaCe0.48Zr0.4Yb0.1Co0.02O3-δ Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: BCZYC2 is a phase pure cubic perovskite and is stable in both humidified H-2 and CO2 at 973 K.
Titulo: Properties and Performance of Anode-Supported Proton-Conducting BaCe0.48Zr0.4Yb0.1Co0.02O3-δ Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The total dc conductivity of BCZYC2 measured in humidified H-2 was 2.1 X 10(-3) S/cm at 873 K.
Titulo: Properties and Performance of Anode-Supported Proton-Conducting BaCe0.48Zr0.4Yb0.1Co0.02O3-δ Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The cell performance was measured with humidified H-2 fuel and methanol/water fuel [with varying molar steam:carbon (S:C) ratios] at 873 K.
Titulo: Properties and Performance of Anode-Supported Proton-Conducting BaCe0.48Zr0.4Yb0.1Co0.02O3-δ Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The maximum open-circuit potential (OCP) of 1.04 V was achieved at 873 K in 3% humidified H-2 fuel with an accompanying peak power density of 89 mW/cm(2).
Titulo: Properties and Performance of Anode-Supported Proton-Conducting BaCe0.48Zr0.4Yb0.1Co0.02O3-δ Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The total cell polarization resistance was 0.83 Omega cm(2).
Titulo: Properties and Performance of Anode-Supported Proton-Conducting BaCe0.48Zr0.4Yb0.1Co0.02O3-δ Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Impedance measurements showed decreasing polarization and ohmic resistance with increasing current density.
Titulo: Properties and Performance of Anode-Supported Proton-Conducting BaCe0.48Zr0.4Yb0.1Co0.02O3-δ Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The cell operation via internal steam reforming of methanol was demonstrated using a methanol/water feed with 3:1 and 2:1 S:C ratios; however, the OCP was reduced to 0.97 and 0.95 V and the peak power density decreased to 65 and 58 mW/cm(2), respectively.
Titulo: Properties and Performance of Anode-Supported Proton-Conducting BaCe0.48Zr0.4Yb0.1Co0.02O3-δ Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: This was primarily attributed to a lower H-2 concentration in the feed stream.
